metadata.description: The Franken Honorary Collection recognizes individuals who have made significant contributions to the web3 community. These individuals are leaders and innovators, and their dedication and passion is admired by the FrankenPunks community. We are proud to honor their contributions and show our appreciation for their hard work and dedication. This collection serves as a tribute to their incredible achievements and inspires others to follow in their footsteps and make their own mark in the world of web3.
